The paper discusses the use of deep neural networks in various machine learning tasks, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The focus of the paper is on adversarial attacks and defenses in images, graphs, and text, which suggests that it could also be classified under "Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition" (cs.CV), "Cryptography and Security" (cs.CR), "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI), and "Computation and Language" (cs.CL).
